java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible
public class AppInterface
extends javax.swing.JPanel

AppInterface Class extends JPanel This class contains all visual components of the GUI of this application. The DayCounterApp class handles all events caused by the components within this JPanel.
